  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    This task defines the guided procedure for identifying and specifying business requirements. This model is used to&#xD;
    specify the requirements.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The Requirements Model defines the requirements, their relations and relevant use cases.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <sections xmi:id="_q8YGMG-8Ed6zv6nlDL4ZGQ" name="1. Create Requirements Container." guid="_q8YGMG-8Ed6zv6nlDL4ZGQ">
    <sectionDescription>The requirements may be structured / categorized and stored in specific containers. For example, a requirement for&#xD;
&quot;technological independence&quot; can be categorized and stored in &quot;Non-functional Requirements&quot; container.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_H5VkwG-9Ed6zv6nlDL4ZGQ" name="2. Create Requirements Diagram." guid="_H5VkwG-9Ed6zv6nlDL4ZGQ">
    <sectionDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The requirements diagram helps to specify the requirements and their relations. In order to relate requiremens the&#xD;
    following links are available:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &quot;part of&quot;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &quot;derive&quot;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &quot;satisfy&quot;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &quot;verify&quot;. This link can be used to indicate which use-case verifies the requirement&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &quot;refine&quot;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        All model elements may be related with the &quot;traceability&quot; links and described using &quot;note&quot; elements.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_zsie0G-9Ed6zv6nlDL4ZGQ" name="3. Create Requirement." guid="_zsie0G-9Ed6zv6nlDL4ZGQ">
    <sectionDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The requirement is defined with a textual desciption. The following properties can be specified:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Name&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Origin&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Benifit, &quot;Critical|Major|Minor&quot;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Cost&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Risk, &quot;Low|Medium|High&quot;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Stability, &quot;Low|High&quot;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Target Release&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Text, detailed textual description of the requirement&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <purpose>&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        To identify&amp;nbsp;and specify business requirements.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
